The ball goes to Jiang Bohan.

7
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,800
Jiang Bohan drives down the right side.

8
00:00:31,910 --> 00:00:33,380
Double-team coming in.

9
00:00:33,660 --> 00:00:36,520
He passes to the weak side—Chen Sujie with the shot!

10
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:46,030
Jingcai has tied the score!

11
00:00:46,580 --> 00:00:49,830
And they have a chance to win the game
with a free throw!

12
00:00:51,650 --> 00:00:53,300
Nanli commits a hand-check foul.

13
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:55,190
Jingcai gets a free throw.

14
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,520
This shot could secure the victory!

15
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,850
But can Chen Sujie do it?

16
00:00:58,430 --> 00:00:59,840
