-Game-winner!

18
00:01:04,019 --> 00:01:05,019
Don't be nervous.

19
00:01:06,420 --> 00:01:07,070
Relax.

20
00:01:09,990 --> 00:01:11,260
Show your true level.

21
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,210
You've got this.

22
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,050
I believe in you.

23
00:02:09,970 --> 00:02:12,670
As the saying goes, "Were I to gain a sword
of gleaming steel,

24
00:02:12,670 --> 00:02:16,530
I would, drunk with might, cleave the sky
and bring down the rainbow!"

25
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:19,380
At this moment, they rewrote team history

26
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,010
and found redemption.

27
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:24,360
Only by facing challenges head-on with courage

28
00:02:24,380 --> 00:02:26,350
can one gain the favor of destiny.

29
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,110
Let's congratulate Jingcai College

30
00:02:28,110 --> 00:02:32,390
on winning this year's Youth Basketball League championship!

31
