We won!

43
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:08,310
Now it's your turn!

44
00:03:10,650 --> 00:03:11,440
You can do it!

45
00:03:11,790 --> 00:03:13,520
Steady breathing, don't rush!

46
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:14,490
Keep going!

47
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:16,079
Come on, Corn!

48
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,300
Two kilometers left!

49
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,290
I'll be waiting for you at the finish line!

50
00:03:19,290 --> 00:03:20,220
You've got this!

51
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:24,980
That 20 km split was 30 seconds faster than usual.

52
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:26,960
Just a little more, Yu Mingxi!

53
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,760
Already one minute and forty-five seconds faster!

54
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,020
Keep going, Yu Mingxi!

55
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:32,910
Come on!

56
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,800
Fifty meters left!

57
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,520
Come on, Mingxi!

58
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,360
Come on, Yu Mingxi!

59
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,079
Go, Corn!

60
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:36,800
Keep going!

61
